nodes.title: ABSYNTH FINETUNE
widgets_values:
## WAN 2.2 S2V ABSYNTH FINETUNE


Finetuned for making music videos.

IMPORTANT:
For the best Lipsync: in Rife set multiplier 2 and scale factor to 1.  In VHS Combine, you have to set the framerat to 32. S2V was trained with 16fps so in the Videocombine you need twice as much frames = 32.

Video Length: in length setting do 91 and in extend 81 <- works great and fast on rtx5060 ti 16gb vram.

Use the pruned loras and best keep the settings from my workflow. 

You can use a video to control the movement.

Only adjust the settings for your video and audio.

==========================================

If you like this finetune
subscribe to my YouTube Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/@Electric-Dreamz

Get my Filmlook Creator Node for Comfy:

https://github.com/Absynth-Vibe-Coding/Comfy-UI-Nodes/
